name: Baby Boys Printed Cotton Kurta with White Pyjama Dress (5-6 Years, Blue)
reviews:
i recently purchased this yellow kurta for my kid and i must say that i am completely satisfied with my purchase the kurta is not only visually appealing with its bright and cheerful shade of yellow but it is also incredibly comfortable for my child to wear

the fabric is of high quality and is soft to the touch making it easy for my child to move around in the kurta is also very well made with sturdy stitching that ensures that it will last through many wears and washes
